---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Host an Event" description="Everything your chapter needs to run a Democracy on Draft event — bingo cards, social media copy, a step-by-step planning guide, and more.">
  <Nav />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label">Free Event Kit</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight text-white mb-4">Democracy on Draft:<br />Protect the<br />Forest Service</h1>
      <div class="blue-rule"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-4">Everything your chapter needs to host your own Democracy on Draft event — a casual evening at a local brewery where neighbors make calls to their representatives, sign petitions, and go home knowing they did something.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mb-8">Download the bingo card, grab the social copy, and follow the planning guide. No experience required.</p>
      <a href="#downloads" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-5">Get the Free Kit &darr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Event Poster -->
  <section class="bg-navy-brand py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center">
      <div class="shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/images/democracy-on-draft-poster-alibi-truckee.png"
          alt="Democracy on Draft: Protect Your Forests event poster — Thursday May 14th, 6PM at Alibi Truckee"
          class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-72"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sky-bright text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Example Event</p>
        <h2 class="text-white font-black text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">This Is What It Looks Like</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Indivisible Tahoe Truckee hosted a Democracy on Draft event at Alibi Truckee — neighbors gathering over beers to call Congress, sign petitions, and fight glyphosate spraying and Forest Service restructuring together.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">Your chapter can do the same. The kit below has everything you need to run your own event.</p>
        <a href="#downloads" class="inline-block mt-6 btn-primary">Get the Free Kit &darr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Downloads -->
  <section id="downloads" class="bg-navy-brand py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label text-center">Free Downloads</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white text-center mb-3">Everything You Need</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-center mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto">Download, print, and use. All materials are free to adapt and share.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-2">Bingo Card</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6 flex-1">One per attendee. 16 civic actions including calling your senator, signing petitions, writing a postcard, and tagging an outdoor brand. Print 50–75 per event.</p>
          <a href="/downloads/Democracy_on_Draft_Bingo_Card.pdf" download class="btn-primary text-sm">Download PDF &darr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📱</div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-2">Social Media Copy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6 flex-1">A full library of caption templates, post copy, and hashtags. Organized by timing (save the date, reminder, day-of, recap) with playful, urgent, and newcomer-friendly variants.</p>
          <a href="#social-copy" class="btn-primary text-sm">View Copy &darr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📋</div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-2">Planning Guide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6 flex-1">A complete step-by-step playbook — venue selection, volunteer roles, promotion timeline, run of show, and troubleshooting. Everything you need from 6 weeks out to post-event.</p>
          <a href="#planning-guide" class="btn-primary text-sm">Read the Guide &darr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bingo Card Preview -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label text-center">Preview</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white text-center mb-8">The Bingo Card</h2>
      <iframe
        src="/downloads/Democracy_on_Draft_Bingo_Card.pdf"
        class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10"
        style="height: 700px;"
        title="Democracy on Draft Bingo Card Preview"
      ></iframe>
      <div class="text-center mt-6">
        <a href="/downloads/Democracy_on_Draft_Bingo_Card.pdf" download class="btn-primary">Download PDF &darr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Online Action Resources -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label">Online Actions</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-3">Resources for Your Action Table</h2>
      <div class="blue-rule"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl">At the event, attendees complete bingo squares using these resources. Have these links open on a tablet or laptop at your action table.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <a href="https://5calls.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card hover:border hover:border-sky transition-all block">
          <h3 class="text-sky-bright font-black text-lg mb-2">5calls.org</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Scripted calls to your representatives. The fastest way to contact Congress — takes under 2 minutes. Scripts provided for Forest Service issues.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://saveusfs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card hover:border hover:border-sky transition-all block">
          <h3 class="text-sky-bright font-black text-lg mb-2">SaveUSFS.org</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Leave a public comment about what the Forest Service means to you. Comment on the proposed restructuring and budget cuts.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://outdooralliance.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card hover:border hover:border-sky transition-all block">
          <h3 class="text-sky-bright font-black text-lg mb-2">Outdoor Alliance</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Action alerts for the outdoor recreation community. Petitions, calls to action, and updates on public lands policy.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://indivisible.org/act" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card hover:border hover:border-sky transition-all block">
          <h3 class="text-sky-bright font-black text-lg mb-2">Indivisible Action</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Current campaigns and action alerts from Indivisible national. Find petitions, postcards, and targeted ask campaigns.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Planning Guide -->
  <section id="planning-guide" class="bg-navy-mid py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label">Step-by-Step Guide</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-3">How to Run a Democracy on Draft Event</h2>
      <div class="blue-rule"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-12">A turnkey playbook for hosting a casual, high-impact civic action night at your local outdoor brewery, taproom, or community gathering space.</p>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-sky text-white font-black text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Phase 1</span>
          <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl">Day Of</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-sky/30">
          <h4 class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-3">Sample 2-hour run of show</h4>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">5:30 PM</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Setup complete, soft opening. Volunteers in place, welcoming atmosphere.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">6:00 PM</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Official start. Greeter signs people in and explains the bingo card. Floater introduces newcomers.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">6:15 PM</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Optional 3-minute welcome. Name the issue of the night. Point to the action table. Keep it under 3 minutes.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">6:20–7:30</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Action time. People work through bingo squares at their own pace. Calling coach helps anyone making their first call.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">7:30 PM</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Optional bingo prizes or raffle for chapter swag or a gift card.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-sky font-bold text-sm w-20 shrink-0">7:45 PM</span>
              <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Quick thank-you, mention next month's date, encourage email signups.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 4 -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-sky text-white font-black text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Phase 2</span>
          <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl">After the Event</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 pl-4 border-l-2 border-sky/30">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-2">Within 24 hours</h4>
            <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>▸ Post a thank-you on social with photos and stats ("38 people, 22 calls made")</li>
              <li>▸ Send a thank-you email to the venue, tag them on social</li>
              <li>▸ Quick volunteer debrief: what worked, what to change next time</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-2">Track these metrics</h4>
            <ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>▸ Total attendance and new chapter signups</li>
              <li>▸ Calls made to Congress, postcards written, petitions signed</li>
              <li>▸ Social media reach and follower growth</li>
              <li>▸ Repeat attendees vs. first-timers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-6 border border-sky/20">
        <p class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Remember: Done is better than perfect.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">The first event will not be perfect. Run it anyway, learn what works, and improve next month. The goal is consistency, not polish.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social Media Copy -->
  <section id="social-copy" class="bg-navy py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label">Social Media</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-3">Ready-to-Use Post Copy</h2>
      <div class="blue-rule"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-10">Replace all <strong class="text-white">[BRACKETS]</strong> with your event details before posting. Mix and match hashtags — use 3–5 per post.</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">

        <!-- Post 1 -->
        <div class="post-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10" style="background: #1C2333;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-white/5">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-navy-brand rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sky-bright font-black text-xs shrink-0">YCN</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold leading-tight">Your Chapter Name</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">3 weeks before your event · 🌐</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-sky-bright font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-navy px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Save the Date</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-4">
            <p class="post-text text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">🍺 New month, new chance to make some calls.

Democracy on Draft is back at [VENUE] on [DATE] at [TIME]. Grab a beer, make a few calls to your reps, sign some petitions, and be home in time for bedtime stories.

No experience required. Scripts provided. First-timers strongly encouraged.

RSVP in our bio.

#DemocracyOnDraft #[YourChapterTag] #5Calls</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-slate-600 text-xs select-none">
              <span>👍 Like</span><span>💬 Comment</span><span>↗ Share</span>
            </div>
            <button class="copy-btn text-xs text-sky font-bold hover:text-sky-light transition-colors">Copy Text</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 2 -->
        <div class="post-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10" style="background: #1C2333;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-white/5">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-navy-brand rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sky-bright font-black text-xs shrink-0">YCN</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold leading-tight">Your Chapter Name</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">3 weeks before your event · 🌐</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-sky-bright font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-navy px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Save the Date</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-4">
            <p class="post-text text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">Public lands are under attack. Your representatives need to hear from you.

Join us [DATE] at [VENUE] for Democracy on Draft — a casual evening of taking real action with your neighbors. We'll show you exactly who to call and what to say.

Show up. Speak up. We'll have your back (and maybe a pint waiting).

#DemocracyOnDraft #PublicLandsForAll #SaveOurForests</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-slate-600 text-xs select-none">
              <span>👍 Like</span><span>💬 Comment</span><span>↗ Share</span>
            </div>
            <button class="copy-btn text-xs text-sky font-bold hover:text-sky-light transition-colors">Copy Text</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 3 -->
        <div class="post-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10" style="background: #1C2333;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-white/5">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-navy-brand rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sky-bright font-black text-xs shrink-0">YCN</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold leading-tight">Your Chapter Name</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">1 week before your event · 🌐</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-sky-bright font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-navy px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Reminder</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-4">
            <p class="post-text text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">Wondering what Democracy on Draft is actually like? Here's the deal:

✅ You walk in, get a beer
✅ We give you a bingo card with civic actions to complete
✅ Make a quick call (we have scripts)
✅ Sign a petition or two
✅ Hang out with neighbors who care about the same things you do
✅ Go home knowing you did something

[DATE] at [VENUE].</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-slate-600 text-xs select-none">
              <span>👍 Like</span><span>💬 Comment</span><span>↗ Share</span>
            </div>
            <button class="copy-btn text-xs text-sky font-bold hover:text-sky-light transition-colors">Copy Text</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 4 -->
        <div class="post-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10" style="background: #1C2333;">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-white/5">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-navy-brand rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sky-bright font-black text-xs shrink-0">YCN</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold leading-tight">Your Chapter Name</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Use anytime · 🌐</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-sky-bright font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-navy px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Evergreen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-4">
            <p class="post-text text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">Since early 2025, the U.S. Forest Service has lost roughly 7,500 employees through layoffs and buyouts — about a quarter of the workforce. The agency manages 193 million acres of public land, including the trails you hike, the campgrounds you camp at, and the wildfire crews that protect your community.

This is not normal. And it's not too late.

Take 90 seconds: 5calls.org · saveusfs.org

#SaveOurForests #PublicLandsForAll</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-slate-600 text-xs select-none">
              <span>👍 Like</span><span>💬 Comment</span><span>↗ Share</span>
            </div>
            <button class="copy-btn text-xs text-sky font-bold hover:text-sky-light transition-colors">Copy Text</button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.copy-btn').forEach(btn => {
          btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const text = btn.closest('.post-card').querySelector('.post-text').innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
              btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
              setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = 'Copy Text'; }, 2000);
            });
          });
        });
      </script>

      <div class="mt-10 card">
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Hashtag Library</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-2">Event</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">#DemocracyOnDraft<br />#BrewsAndDemocracy<br />#CivicHour</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-2">Public Lands</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">#PublicLandsForAll<br />#SaveOurForests<br />#SaveUSFS<br />#KeepPublicLandsPublic</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sky-bright font-bold mb-2">Action</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">#5Calls<br />#CallYourReps<br />#Indivisible<br />#IndivisibleNation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
